{
  "stem": "14613.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We found out that the camp is being evacuated to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they did is-- this camp consisted also-- the big camp consisted of both Jews and Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what they did, they asked all the Jews to go separately.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took the Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were the first ones to, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to get out from the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that point, my brother and myself decided we were going to hide among the gentiles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We hid ourselves among the Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] shortly thereafter, they took-- and I noticed a lot of Jewish people hid themself among the Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because it was already disorganized at that point.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't know exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were able to, to wrap all of the means of-- wherever there was some food-- the kitchen, the warehouses, everything-- each one of us whatever could take some food took with us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then, they divided the balance of the people in the, in the camp into groups of about 4,000.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they started to marching us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Basically, we were, we were walking at night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And during the day, they would surround us, most of the time, on a, in a little hillside in the forest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they surrounded-- the Germans surrounded us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we stayed there during the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was raining, pouring.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were tired, walking all night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we fell down wherever we could, and we slept, whatever it was, in the mud.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We had-- you know, all the time that I was in the camp, my brother and myself, we were always together.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We never separated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were times where they wanted to separate us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
